title: Hour 2: Air Bud, Horror Movie
description:
The team does a comprehensive breakdown of the current state of Horror movies, we bring you a Thursday Thunder, and Mahmoud Abdul-Rauf joins to talk his new autobiography In the Blink of an Eye and being named Jamal Crawford's top bucket getter of all time.
